                                <p>The precursor to bidding is registration. So if you have not yet registered please register yourself. Placing a bid is simple. If you have to bid higher than the previous bid then just click on “Out Bid” button. </p>

                                <p>To participate in the auction the system will then prompt you to pay nominal fee of Rs 499/- (auction participation fee). This is only for the first bid on the unit. You will not be prompted for fee for subsequent bid on a unit. Remember all bids are only on the base price per sq ft and outbidding will be by a pre-determined amount per sq foot. Bidding is in steps of Rs 25 on the base price. The auction is live for 14 days so you can place the bids anytime during those 14 days.</p>
